Helen Gibson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Gibson 0 Helen Gibson (August 27, 1892 – October 10, 1977) was an American film actress, vaudeville performer, radio performer, film producer, trick rider and rodeo performer; and is considered to be the first American professional stunt woman.
